The goal is to get every Wallet + Exchange to support the open payment standards manifested in our products + tools. They don't need to run our software, but they should support these protocols and believe that we can get millions of developers and people doing the same.

curl --location --request POST 'https://hermes-rest.ilpv4.dev/accounts' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--header 'Accept: application/json' \
--data-raw '{
  "assetCode": "XRP",
  "assetScale": "6"
}'

